As you may already know, emacs is more than a (cross-platform) text editor. Some say that it is like a whole operating system (and some [devil worshippers](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Editor_war#Humour) say that it lacks a good text editor...). For the next 30 days (starting December 1, 2010) I'll check it as well as I can. I will work just with emacs.  
  
You can check the challenge updates below:  
[](http://www.mostlymaths.net/2010/12/emacs-30-day-challenge-update-1-writing.html)

