*   Update #2: [Using gnus to read mail (in particular gmail)](http://www.mostlymaths.net/2010/12/emacs-30-day-challenge-using-gnus-to.html)  
    
*   Update #3: [A glimpse of bbdb: the insidious Big Brother Database and gnus](http://www.mostlymaths.net/2010/12/emacs-30-day-challenge-glimpse-of-bbdb.html)
